1. Specify the cluster configuration in ansible_hosts
2. Run . ENV
3. Edit the configuration in multinode/hadoop-1.2.1/conf/*
4. Login into the namenode 
   And prepare password ssh to all data nodes manually
   for dn in datanode1 datanode2 datanode3 ...
   do 
     echo Data Node $dn
     ssh-copy-id $dn
     # ssh-copy-id $dn.daddylabs.com
   done
5. Run the scripts in the numbered order
6. Have fun!

Good luck!

Dinesh

